      <title>AI Fever扫荡中国的政治烦恼，助长了技术乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/deepseek-fueled-ai-fever-injects-new-energy-into-china-s-npc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来，中国对国家立法机关的年度聚会一直是纪律严明且精心编排的事务。它的柔和的共鸣实际上是对国内停滞的加深关注的回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-11/deepseek-fueled-ai-fever-injects-new-energy-into-china-s-npc</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 02:30:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥说，乌克兰会议试图澄清什么可能。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/ukraine-meeting-aims-to-clarify-possible-concessions-rubio-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿马可·卢比奥（Marco Rubio）说，在朝着与俄罗斯停火时可能会有什么可能的让步，旨在阐明美国和乌克兰在沙特阿拉伯周二的会谈，旨在阐明重大突破的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-10/ukraine-meeting-aims-to-clarify-possible-concessions-rubio-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Mar 2025 18:20:58 GMT</pubDate>
